Introduction

SeeA (시아; formerly known as Eunyoung) is a South Korean rapper and singer currently under MyDoll Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group PinkFantasy, its sub-units PinkFantasy SHY and PinkFantasy Shadow, and a former member of Piggy Dolls as Eunyoung (은영).
